name: Sepertiga Malam
description:
"Sepertiga Malam" its means "One-third of the Night" in English. This story is a parable of various night activities when many people are asleep, various stories of people who feel defeated, feeling alone, and also stories full of spirituality and religiosity.One thing that should not be forgotten, even though the night is quiet sometimes brings a lot of hope.



Sepertiga Malam adalah perumpamaan tentang berbagai kegiatan malam ketika banyak orang tertidur, berbagai cerita dari orang-orang yang merasa kalah, merasa sendiri, dan juga cerita penuh spiritualitas dan religiositas. Satu hal yang jangan dilupakan, malam walau sunyi kadang membawa banyak harapan.
